flowchart LR
  A[Order Placed] --> B[Validate Payment]
  B --> C{Payment Approved?}
  C -- No --> D[Notify Failure]
  C -- Yes --> E[Reserve Inventory]
  E --> F{Stock Available?}
  F -- No --> G[Backorder Queue]
  F -- Yes --> H[Pack Shipment]
  H --> I[Dispatch Carrier]
  I --> J[Send Tracking Email]
